snippet.title: The Voidness - Announce Trailer 2023 (Horror LIDAR Game)
snippet.description:
WISHLIST IT ON STEAM ►► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2276850/The_Voidness__Lidar_Psychological_Survival_Horror_Game/?beta=0

Official reveal and announcement trailer for The Voidness, a psychological horror game I have been working on where you have to scan the environment to see. Try and escape The Voidness, but you are not alone...

Release Date: MARCH 17, 2023.

WISHLIST IT ON STEAM ►► https://store.steampowered.com/app/2276850/The_Voidness__Lidar_Psychological_Survival_Horror_Game/?beta=0

IndieDB ► https://www.indiedb.com/games/the-voidness-lidar-psychological-survival-horror-game

Thanks so much for your support, really appreciate it!

• Website: https://steelkrill.com
• Twitter:  https://twitter.com/steelkrill

#gaming #horrorgamestamillive #horrorgames2023 #horrorgaming #horrorstories #scary #lidar 

Music is composed and created by Fuzzeke.
